<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, man sagt vast
                                                  <add>bey uns</add> lantmansweise, wie unser
                                                  <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>,
                                                  <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> künig, von
                                                  <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> herauf cziehet, des
                                                wir doch noch kein
                                                  <expan>eige<ex>n</ex>sch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.
                                                  <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, ob ir des iht
                                                eigenschaft west <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> was ir
                                                  <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> het, daz
                                                ir uns das an <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> brief
                                                bey <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<add><expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan></add>
<expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                                                wöllet, und ob ir des noch kein
                                                  <expan>eige<ex>n</ex>sch<ex>aft</ex></expan> het,
                                                wenn ir des <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>fürb<ex>as</ex></expan> ein eigenschaft
                                                erfüret, daz ir uns das bey ewrselbs
                                                  <expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                                                wöllet, dem wir das lon
                                                  <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllen. Das
                                                  <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir in
                                                  <expan>sölich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                                  <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
